This app developed to show the Weather updated for every 2 hour period, This App designed as MVP with followed by repository pattern.
API Used: http://openweathermap.org/
For testing purpose we are fetching water updated for the below details:
ZIP code : 94040
Location : US
REST Client used here : Retrofit
Design Patterns used here : MVP
For periodic call app used Work Manager.
Added Test case for MyPresenter.

Upcoming Release Notes:
1.App future release we need to enhance the UI as per the UAT feedback.
2.Need to show some more information about the weather.
3.In upcoming release will provide option to select his/her location to get the weather update.
3.Need to achieve 100% test case coverage for all the testable class.